      "title": "There is no train to Colombo tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Railway Deputy General Manager (Traffic) Mr. Gamini Seneviratne said tonight that due to the imposition of police curfew on 7 police divisions in the Western Province, trains will not run to Colombo tomorrow (9)."
